claim: Flublok ensures identical antigenic match with WHO- and FDA-selected flu strains.
explanation: Flow chart of subject participation in the study showing numbers randomized into treatment groups and included in the safety populations (n=2344 and n=2304). does not support the claim because the figure only presents participant randomization and safety population numbers, with no information on antigenic matching or WHO/FDA-selected flu strains. Note: Limited to a flow chart of enrollment; no immunogenicity or antigen match data are presented.
